OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Fergus
OL,7,FHarris
OL,9,FSaturday will mark the end of 'dry
OL,10,FJanuary' for many, but returning
OL,11,Fdrinkers might be surprised when they
OL,12,Fgo to buy their first drink of 2025.
OL,14,FA 1.7 per cent cut in the duty on
OL,15,Fdraught beer means pints pulled in the
OL,16,Fpub (below 8.5% ABV) should be a penny
OL,17,Fcheaper.
OL,19,FIt is the first time in a decade that
OL,20,Ftax on draught alcohol has decreased -
OL,21,Fbut not all drinks are getting cheaper.
