OL,3,CHow do changes in alcohol duty affect
OL,4,Cyou?
OL,6,FThe price of wine and spirits is set
OL,7,Fto rise from Saturday, as an increase
OL,8,Fin tax and duties comes into effect.
OL,10,FAlcohol tax will rise by 3.6 per cent,
OL,11,Fin line with Retail Prices Index
OL,12,Finflation as announced in the Budget
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FAt the same time, a new system to tax
OL,16,Fwines and spirits based on strength
OL,17,Fwill be introduced.
OL,19,FThis means a 40 per cent ABV bottle of
OL,20,Fgin, for example, will be 33p more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
