OL,6,FAnd a 14.5 per cent ABV bottle of wine
OL,7,Fwill increase by 54p.
OL,9,FThe government is also introducing an
OL,10,Fincrease in relief for small producers
OL,11,F"to help small breweries innovate" and
OL,12,F"support economic growth."
OL,14,FAlongside the increase in draught
OL,15,Frelief, these tax cuts are worth #85
OL,16,Fmillion.
