OL,3,CHow do changes in alcohol duty affect
OL,4,Cyou?
OL,6,FExchequer Secretary to the Treasury,
OL,7,FJames Murray said: "Our pubs and
OL,8,Fbrewers are an essential part of the
OL,9,Ffabric of the UK and our brilliant
OL,10,Fhigh streets.
OL,12,F"Through draught relief, small
OL,13,Fproducer relief, and expanding market
OL,14,Faccess for smaller brewers, we will
OL,15,Fhelp boost sector growth and deliver
OL,16,Four Plan for Change to put more money
OL,17,Fin working people's pockets."
OL,19,FBut the UK Spirits Alliance, which
OL,20,Frepresents 300 distillers, disagrees.
