OL,6,FIt has written to the Chancellor
OL,7,Fwarning of the impact on a sector "we
OL,8,Fshould be championing not crushing,"
OL,9,Fand says Saturday's "tax increase
OL,10,Fcould be the final nail in the coffin
OL,11,Ffor many."
OL,13,FIt argues that the "triple-whammy" of
OL,14,F"duty hikes, tax rises, and spiralling
OL,15,Fbusiness costs are forcing distillers
OL,16,Fto shut down".
OL,18,FA survey of 4,000 people commissioned
OL,19,Fby the group found that 77 per cent of
OL,20,Fpub managers believe the hike in
OL,21,Fspirits duty will damage business.
