OL,6,FAnd 88 per cent of bar owners and
OL,7,Fpublicans think the cut in duty on
OL,8,Fdraught beer will have no impact.
OL,10,FCopper Rivet is a family-run
OL,11,Fdistillery in Chatham, Kent. It closed
OL,12,Fits restaurant after the October
OL,13,Fbudget, blaming it for "significantly
OL,14,Fincreasing operational costs and
OL,15,Fworsening the business outlook,
OL,16,Fpushing the restaurant's viability
OL,17,Fbeyond reach."
