OL,3,CHow do changes in alcohol duty affect
OL,4,Cyou?
OL,6,FAhead of Saturday's changes to alcohol
OL,7,Fduty, Stephen Russell, the
OL,8,FDistillery's Managing Director, told
OL,9,FITV News: "The spirits industry in
OL,10,Fthis country is a massive success and
OL,11,Fit's an incredible exporter.
OL,13,F"And it is completely illogical to
OL,14,Fthink that you are supporting an
OL,15,Findustry by increasing the tax burden
OL,16,Fspecifically targeted at those
OL,17,Fproducts, and then also across the
OL,18,Fboard on overheads like employing
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
