OL,3,CHow do changes in alcohol duty affect
OL,4,Cyou?
OL,6,F"The current duty regime is such that
OL,7,Fa centilitre of alcohol is taxed
OL,8,Fsignificantly more if it appears in a
OL,9,Fbottle of spirits than if it does in a
OL,10,Fcan of beer, which I don't understand.
OL,12,F"It's illogical. This government may
OL,13,Fwant to be pro-growth, but I haven't
OL,14,Fseen anything that they have done in
OL,15,Fparticular in our sphere that is
OL,16,Fsupportive of growth. Frankly the
OL,17,Fopposite".
